Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.02,Op; ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}Čtyři
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:24.36,Op; ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}Tři
